  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large mason jar, combine the millet, water, vegetable broth, carrots, onion, mushrooms, salt, black pepper, and dried thyme.",
    "Stir the mixture well to combine.",
    "Cover the mason jar with a lid and bake for 45 minutes.",
    "Remove the mason jar from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir the pilaf again and serve hot."
